<H2>Equipment - the balanced bar</h2>

<TABLE border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <TR>
    <TD valign="top" width="180">
      <IMG border="0" src="/images/equipment/Image1.gif"><BR>
